                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>wir</add> unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, die sie uns in
              <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe benant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, was der
